      <item>
        <title>Getting Started</title>
        <description>&lt;h2 id=&quot;step-1&quot;&gt;Step 1&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Sign up to our developers &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.bavel.io/developers&quot;&gt;console&lt;/a&gt; to get a developer ID.
&lt;img src=&quot;/images/dev_id.png&quot; alt=&quot;Developers Console&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h2 id=&quot;step-2&quot;&gt;Step 2&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/download-and-install&quot;&gt;Download and implement&lt;/a&gt; our SDK.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h2 id=&quot;step-3&quot;&gt;Step 3&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;After the SDK is implemented, launch your app with it and you should see it in your developer &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.bavel.io/developers&quot;&gt;console&lt;/a&gt; with state “Unverified”.
&lt;img src=&quot;/images/dev_unverified.png&quot; alt=&quot;Developer Unverified&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h2 id=&quot;step-4&quot;&gt;Step 4&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Upload your updated app to the store, and in few hours your app will be verified and you’ll be able to watch states in the developers console.&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
